{"tid":1525782,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【心理戰】立即停用藍黃陣營之分 (轉載)","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:48:30.000Z","uid":30836,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02f0a466aa5aa2dfb6a6c2f29f25dcd38c44499a","tid":1525782,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"原本藍絲帶只係一個不成氣候嘅偽陣營<br />\n只係土共夾硬整出嚟證明香港有班藍絲帶同黃絲帶分庭抗禮<br />\n造成二分天下嘅假象<br />\n並且散播藍黃嘅標籤<br />\n將<span style=\"color: red;\">成件事眨低成只係唔同顏色嘅政見之爭</span>就係佢哋嘅目的<br />\n<br />\n實際上大家都知藍絲帶根本唔係陣營嚟<br />\n佢哋根本冇論述冇目標亦都冇凝聚力同實質動員力<br />\n只係一班為反示威撐政府而存在嘅人<br />\n大家都識得笑佢哋係一車車支那人同老人院送去集會<br />\n點解要將佢哋當真呢？我哋同佢哋嘅分別真係只係顏色？<br />\n<br />\n所謂藍絲有啲係廢中廢老有啲係支那人有啲係黑社會有啲係保皇黨<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋根本唔係有共同目標同內部團結嘅組織<br />\n同我哋作為香港人呢個命運共同體完全唔可以相提並論</span><br />\n要嗌就嗌返廢老、親中、舐共、保皇之類<br />\n唔好再將佢哋當成一個陣營<br />\n咁樣只係間接眨低緊自己<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>作者：木堂</strong><br />\n【心理戰】立即停用藍黃陣營之分<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dKsjKT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dKsjKT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></div></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce901cabb9344bfcb870a09403f33ae613e68a8e","tid":1525782,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"61f2a2529ed43118b3c1ab13a713fe527931439b","tid":1525782,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa5b91dd471ac492fc2e5d92a791b45b9061936","tid":1525782,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"熱烈宣傳中共誠信破產，殘害人民<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕香港成為「反共基地」<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕持續性抗爭<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n覺得岩、有value就做啦<br />\n遊行、連儂、傳單、網絡戰<br />\n<br />\n自由無罪，造反有理<br />\n<br />\nBe water 不被捕 不分化 不割席"},{"pid":"134722d7c7f4f42d229890aefd374a2e4c471d6e","tid":1525782,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"獻世派<br />\n<br />\n反民主人士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe500207ec6df0727d18ed33bf655a83c78425a","tid":1525782,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e57bdc8e98351239bf56f0bdc6e87af1c7bba48c","tid":1525782,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f752bec4d184725d716e9e8bc0b45c765bcb3f","tid":1525782,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid